{"tid":2009293,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有關酷刑 (version 1.1)","createTime":"2020-05-09T15:40:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T05:24:28.000Z","uid":47901,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aa76699314a8942d6f9b98a69ebd3be993ef339a","tid":2009293,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T15:40:21.000Z","msg":"人類一般不會花太多心思去為動物製造酷刑，但卻會為人類花盡心思，錢財，時間，去設計同行使酷刑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國的凌遲是其表表者，可以說是人類酷刑史上的極致<br />\n<br />\n跟據中國凌遲酷刑多年的行使經驗，受刑者受刑之時，雖氣若遊絲，未能反抗，但時以眼神目光望住繪子手，我諗呢個係一個反制，當然繪子手亦有反制方法，可以行使&rdquo;剜目凌遲&ldquo;，即挖掉雙眼，似是大家在&ldquo;鬥法&ldquo;<br />\n<br />\n然而&rdquo;剜目凌遲&ldquo;難度較高，若繪子手經驗不足，手法不夠純熟，或者受刑者體質不夠強健，可能會太快弄死受刑者，所以有時要退而求其次，把額頭的頭皮切割，反下來蓋着受刑者眼睛，當然，代價是向觀眾顯示了自己的&ldquo;技術唔好&ldquo;<br />\n<br />\n如果受刑者就快死，有時會被人餵食食物，給他水解渴，或讓他休一休息，甚致給他止一止痛<br />\n<br />\n明朝宦官劉謹，就類似這樣，因為&ldquo;拖延死亡&rdquo;的工夫做得完善，以致劉謹受刑達數日，在斷氣前一刻，他的身體幾乎被削到如一幅骨架<br />\n<br />\n不可有豬，牛，老虎，白鴿等等被人拿起凌遲示眾吧?"},{"pid":"86c4ba4a7333f2b97302f60e0c476bab032ec9f1","tid":2009293,"uid":47901,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T16:31:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=R5XchEwhmSw&amp;feature=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmusic.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DR5XchEwhmSw%26feature%3Dshare&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=41cb14de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=R5XchEwhmSw&amp;feature=share</a>"},{"pid":"31abdba708de2926bc202c80d44e833ef28723c2","tid":2009293,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T17:18:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=lioSBQwkJ5c&amp;feature=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmusic.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlioSBQwkJ5c%26feature%3Dshare&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpanyrFheAedOz%2Bkyyi3ikZI%3D&h=d946c183\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://music.youtube.com/watch?v=lioSBQwkJ5c&amp;feature=share</a>